01:18:48.790 --> 01:18:51.122
Let's go to the barn.

01:18:54.162 --> 01:18:57.222
They couldn't sell the farm
after what happened.

01:18:57.466 --> 01:19:00.299
It's been empty ever since.

01:19:04.606 --> 01:19:06.699
This is where she was found?

01:19:07.109 --> 01:19:11.637
Yes. Her husband found her.
It was horrific for him. Horrific.

01:19:14.149 --> 01:19:16.140
She was lying right here.

01:19:19.387 --> 01:19:21.184
In this booth.

01:19:21.389 --> 01:19:24.586
Bound and tortured.

01:19:34.402 --> 01:19:37.098
Were the animals also harmed?

01:19:38.173 --> 01:19:40.334
How did you know?

01:19:42.744 --> 01:19:46.180
"If a woman approaches an animal
to have sexual relations with it,

01:19:46.314 --> 01:19:48.805
kill both the woman and the animal."

01:19:52.854 --> 01:19:55.550
- It might be a coincidence.
- Yes.

01:20:00.228 --> 01:20:02.560
Goddamn, Lisbeth.

